expression.expression: CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(SDTRDJ)) IS NULL OR TRIM(SDTRDJ) = '' OR TRIM(SDTRDJ) = '0' THEN NULL ELSE to_timestamp(date_add(cast(substring(SDTRDJ+ 1900000,1,4) AS Date),cast(substring(SDTRDJ,4,3) as int)-1)) end
